{"tid":1217841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(警犬侮辱耶和華) 查咗經，有興趣嘅入嚟一齊聲討警犬","createTime":"2019-06-13T14:10:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T03:41:47.000Z","uid":142348,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"649c0d9f917ccbd7b2db14636096ae10e89a211a","tid":1217841,"uid":142348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:10:32.000Z","msg":"主內連登家各位巴絲平安 !<br />\n<br />\n20多名牧師及傳道人舉行記者招待會，述說6月11日晚至6月12日下午的所見所聞，強烈譴責警方暴力鎮壓和平示威者。數名牧師多番哽咽，其中有牧師聲稱，在請求警察於向前推進或作衝散示威者的行動時作警示，惟警察卻以挑釁口脗說：<span style=\"color: blue;\">「叫你個耶穌落嚟見我哋。」</span><br />\n<br />\n路加福音22:63-65 是這樣說的<br />\n耶穌受戲弄侮辱（&nbsp;太 26:67-68&nbsp;可 14:65&nbsp;）<br />\n看守耶穌的人戲弄他，毆打他。他們蒙著他的眼睛，問他：「猜猜看，是誰打你？」他們又說了許多侮辱他的話。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我以馬太福音5:22 安慰各位<br />\n[但是我告訴你們：所有向他弟兄發怒的，當遭受審判；罵他弟兄『廢物』的，當遭受議會的審判；罵『蠢貨』的，<span style=\"color: red;\">當遭受烈火的地獄</span>。]<br />\n<br />\n不要跟邪惡的人對抗，嘗試以愛感化他們。<br />\n星期日 星期一 以歌聲感化佢哋 !!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n保護左右前後嘅弟兄 讓弟兄免於危險 !<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n主的奴僕<br />\n雙層芝士媽寶"},{"pid":"b0baf3d860c3686f38427a67354283e60896b82a","tid":1217841,"uid":142348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:12:06.000Z","msg":"唔可以俾耶和華生氣發怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb555b4a923ae9e70f717a8d43f31bc8220035c7","tid":1217841,"uid":142348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:14:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n申命記<br />\n21:18人若有頑梗悖逆的兒子、不聽從父母的話、他們雖懲治他、他仍不聽從。<br />\n21:19父母就要抓住他、將他帶到本地的城門、本城的長老那裡．<br />\n21:20對長老說、我們這兒子頑梗悖逆、不聽從我們的話、是貪食好酒的人。<br />\n21:21<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">本城的眾人就要用石頭將他打死</span>．這樣就把那惡從你們中間除掉．以色列眾人都要聽見害怕。"},{"pid":"de461acc5dc63c897d10e25274db2178e3a08022","tid":1217841,"uid":142348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:14:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f939e69d460d688de87c6efd203ff022522016d","tid":1217841,"uid":142348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:15:31.000Z","msg":"阿里lu yaaaaaaa"},{"pid":"641f8c9f25db3db23283b56b691673b080576adb","tid":1217841,"uid":185290,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:16:07.000Z","msg":"感謝主！令連登仔同耶教關係變好，主能夠！"},{"pid":"bbed31eb2b42f38ef000dfac601390c7f80d9798","tid":1217841,"uid":183971,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:17:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />恰鳩我大佬蘇哥"},{"pid":"801edf503ab72fbc59ce174379452b916e76a2d3","tid":1217841,"uid":183971,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DTLwrAL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDTLwrAL.png&h=1e12b189&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a4b79764f85d3a8a9d3082d2001e9891f8d975e","tid":1217841,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"641f8c9f25db3db23283b56b691673b080576adb","tid":1217841,"uid":185290,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,